> > > + * v1.2 device - SDCA address mapping
> > > + *
> > > + * Spec definition
> > > + *	Bits		Contents
> > > + *	31		0 (required by addressing range)
> > > + *	30:26		0b10000 (Control Prefix)
> > > + *	25		0 (Reserved)
> > > + *	24:22		Function Number [2:0]
> > > + *	21		Entity[6]
> > > + *	20:19		Control Selector[5:4]
> > > + *	18		0 (Reserved)
> > > + *	17:15		Control Number[5:3]
> > > + *	14		Next
> > > + *	13		MBQ
> > > + *	12:7		Entity[5:0]
